│  calculate_from_derived(derived, country_code="US")                          │
│  1. energy_kwh = derived.workload_energy_j / 3.6e6                           │
│  2. Get grid factors from GridFactorManager                                   │
│  3. Calculate:                                                                │
│     • CarbonMetrics(kg = energy_kwh × carbon_factor)                         │
│     • WaterMetrics(liters = energy_kwh × water_factor)                       │
│     • MethaneMetrics(kg = energy_kwh × methane_factor/1000)                  │
│  4. Apply GWP for methane CO₂e equivalents                                   │
